data.title: Netepi-collection
data.description: Communicable disease and epidemiological data collection and management system
data.name: NetEpi-Collection

evidence: README indicates network usage: "3)  Albatross 1.35 or later (Web application framework for Python)"
"NetEpi Collection" is described as an application with user and admin web interfaces (e.g., "access the user and admin apps at URLs similar to...") indicating end-user application software.

The software is a "Network-enabled tools for epidemiology and public health practice" and includes epidemiological functions like epi curve graphs and case-contact visualisation, directly supporting epidemiology/public health research and practice.
